Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:04.14,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon #13 is maintaining \Nits extremely strong force
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.48,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,as it continues making its way up north.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:10.28,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,The storm area struck South Daitou \NIsland last night at around 11 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.78,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, the effect on \Ntransportation in all areas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.32,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.04,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,The TV says the Shinkansen is pooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.92,0:00:28.59,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Not pooping! Operating!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:29.88,Caption Top,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}[ Note: unko suru = pooping, \Nunkou suru = in operation ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:29.88,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Pooping?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.38,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Operating!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:35.22,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,They probably said, "The Shinkansen \Nis operating on normal schedules."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.35,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,That means it's running same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.39,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinkansen is pooping!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:52.19,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go poop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.99,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.79,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,Typhoon #13 has changed course \Nand is gradually moving east,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:03.58,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,where it's expected to make \Nlandfall in the Tokai area
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:05.83,Main Dialog,Newscaster,0000,0000,0000,,sometime between this \Nevening and tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:08.38,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,She said there's a typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:12.00,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Typhoons \Ncome every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.42,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:16.97,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of TP?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.55,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,You should see how much I'm making!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.51,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Bring a ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.52,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are notoriously childish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.98,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can empathize.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.07,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:44.20,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,It's different than a sacrifice. Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:47.87,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's like some penalty game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:51.13,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,So, why? I don't get it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:56.22,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little bit unsatisfied, but your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:02:00.18,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,right now is more than just important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.22,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.48,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,as something never-ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:13.69,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Crying isn't painful, it's love's sweet drops, sweet drops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.82,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep dreaming forever, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:20.28,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be more kind, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.87,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I’m with you, I’m happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:27.37,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Girls sure are strong, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:30.62,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes we're weak, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:36.88,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Our wish is to be happy, happy, happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:40.84,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,And those days will be happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:48.43,Opening Song,Opening Song,0000,0000,0000,,Just wanna make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.62,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.46,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.00,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.71,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:18.13,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:20.63,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:36.48,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave just enough \Nspace for the circles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.03,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,it means you've written \Nit in a cool way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:38.73,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.86,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, how much is "just enough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.11,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.95,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,How many centimeters? \NHow many millimeters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.59,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to draw these circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.30,Main Dialog,Class,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.47,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the rest \Nwill be your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.72,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,For the next activity, all the \Nfirst-graders are going to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.35,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Meet up outside in front \Nof your own morning glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.64,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.31,Main Dialog,Class,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.20,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Sandbags are that heavy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.78,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's still morning and \NI'm already beat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:32.16,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,And it had to be on a day like today \Nthat we've got tons of samples to ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.29,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.25,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.97,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,My kids' educational insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.26,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Your kids are still babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.43,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,If I waited 'til they got bigger, \Nthe insurance wouldn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:51.85,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:54.18,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,We're enrolled too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.77,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I kinda doubt he'll be \Ncollege material, being my kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.77,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,We got two, so it's pretty tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.78,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Ours is still a little squirt, \Nso we got day-care fees too,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.78,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,which is nothin' to sneeze at.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.91,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,And he outgrows his clothes like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.74,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're only contract \Nemployees, but it helps
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:14.41,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,that the welfare pension program \Nand health insurance are included.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.92,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,How about life insurance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.92,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,My wife took care of \Nthat behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.59,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,For mine, the payout is \Ndecent if I kick the bucket,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.17,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,but she has universal life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.05,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,The basic one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.09,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys really are "Dads", aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.60,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.02,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothin' to be impressed about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.89,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much insurance costs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.69,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,The brat next door is so \Nfrickin' noisy, we wanna move,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:42.36,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,but the money just ain't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.24,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I don't even know \Nwhat I'm workin' for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.57,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.37,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,You get married, this is what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.79,Main Dialog,Mayunashi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a girlfriend, \Nso no danger of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.04,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,They're always bitching \Nand moaning, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:01.92,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, there's a \Nsense of security...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:07.55,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine them \Nbecoming like Rin's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.70,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.74,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.67,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.59,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What about your drawing board?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.84,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... The ground is flat, \Nso I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.14,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,That's not gonna float!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.97,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,When I tell you to bring \Nsomething, you bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.98,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Get it right now! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.73,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, your drawing is \Nreally good, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.36,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.69,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.28,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.16,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,That really is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.91,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,The colors of this flower and this \Nflower are slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:22.67,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,and Rin-san's drawing shows that with \Nboth bluish and purplish colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.17,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You have a sharp eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.80,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun and those boys \Nare wandering around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:42.98,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.61,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's drawing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.15,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-san, your morning \Nglories are looking splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.82,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a waste not to sketch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.12,Main Dialog,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-san, do you like drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.79,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,So-so, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.08,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.21,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:08.05,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-san, why do you always, \Nalways disturb everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.13,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Now sit down and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.63,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And don't make a weird face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.98,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,I got Kouki's hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.15,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.07,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Kouki-san! Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.28,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.16,Main Dialog,Female Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.62,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.50,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.00,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.34,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down and draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.47,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get you in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.39,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.57,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,That was incredible, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:20.45,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun always does strange stuff and \Nhe's scary when he loses his temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:23.41,Main Dialog,Sayaka,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan, he'll bully you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.96,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,No, he won't! After all, we went \Nto the same nursery school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.17,Main Dialog,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.19,Main Dialog,Beanpole,0000,0000,0000,,They're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.32,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys pick up your \Nkids at 6 too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.82,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Cuttin' it close today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.53,Main Dialog,Mayunashi,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.87,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's get it done in one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.96,Main Dialog,Kurokamihige,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.30,Main Dialog,Instructors 1 and 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:21.01,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,You got a little wet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.93,Main Dialog,Instructor 1,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan! Your father's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.10,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:28.73,Main Dialog,Instructor 1,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.73,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:33.11,Main Dialog,Instructor 1,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.44,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's really picked up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:40.24,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I wish I could've \Ngotten here earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.87,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the last?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.83,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun is here, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.16,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.41,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,There's a storm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:49.71,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's really coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.26,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:02.93,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.93,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,An umbrella's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.73,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.35,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-uh. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.48,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.57,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.13,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:37.13,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.76,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:47.10,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but it's already decided \Nhow he gets home, so we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:51.52,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I know. But the wind is only \Nto keep getting stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.86,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,so let me try calling Nitani-san \Nand see if it would be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.44,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Then, just to confirm, can I \Nhand the phone over to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.90,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,Um... In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.32,Main Dialog,Instructor 1,0000,0000,0000,,We can go home early, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:05.41,Main Dialog,Instructor 2,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.87,Main Dialog,Instructors 1 and 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.73,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.89,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.35,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.70,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.37,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Get behind me and follow along!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.37,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:58.38,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:00.92,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,The storm windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.94,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.57,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Careful, don't catch your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.03,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.01,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, it's kind of like a secret base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.85,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,It's in my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.81,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna rinse it now, \Nso don't open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.44,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right, dry the rest yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.78,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi, your back is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.91,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.58,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening! It's Nitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.88,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.59,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} able to \Nget off work early...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.01,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I overstepped my bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:32.47,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! It was a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.64,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Kouki got soaked \Non the way here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:39.85,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I don't know where \Nto begin to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:50.07,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.16,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi, let me borrow yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.54,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Again with that?! You say, \N"Daikichi-san", right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:59.75,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,He said "Daikichi" is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:03.17,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm more comfortable with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:03.96,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.30,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Just "Daikichi" is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.06,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan, you're good at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.77,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I can use a knife, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:21.65,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're already a young lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.52,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi does the fire, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.69,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.74,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You never help out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.07,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.87,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you my knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:41.25,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Onions are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.59,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch! Wash your eyes right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.38,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.42,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I'm crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.01,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,You're making hamburger patties...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:01.14,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Yep... It looks delicious, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.61,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,These are kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.07,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,They're not strange! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.61,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure they'll taste fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:14.11,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan! The eggs are boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:15.66,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please peel them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:17.70,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:24.67,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.79,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're so good at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.09,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin is eating it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.34,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki, do you love your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:42.14,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,If only she weren't such an old nag...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:51.32,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a sense of security here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.45,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,This one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.83,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What about giving thanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.12,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food \Nwe're about to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.33,Main Dialog,All,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food \Nwe're about to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.77,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki, use your chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.64,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'm just getting it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.78,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.41,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}is{\i0} good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:41.62,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Food tastes better when \Nwe eat it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.75,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat here again tomorrow night!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.04,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.97,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.97,0:17:59.51,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:00.93,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.48,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,And then it hit him right in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.48,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He's so excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:16.20,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was never able to give him this \Nkind of opportunity 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.07,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy about this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.78,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:23.41,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't... I need to thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.54,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said we didn't \Nneed those circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.83,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Being able to see that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.67,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got off work early.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.42,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,She's raising a child alone, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.39,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Daikichi! Come here a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.81,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.11,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.73,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I call a taxi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.15,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.07,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.28,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.91,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Reina-chan \Nand her mom stayed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.62,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,That was different!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:13.21,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,See ya tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:14.63,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:15.55,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.05,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.88,Main Dialog,Kouki's Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.97,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,We had fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:23.97,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.51,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.48,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:39.00,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,A sunny early Sunday afternoon
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:42.05,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go somewhere today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:48.85,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same road I'm used to traveling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:53.44,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see it sparkling so bright
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:58.94,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0010,0000,,With the sun shining down its warmth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.86,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,And you here by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:08.58,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already high, high, high
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:14.25,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like dashing out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.71,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Sing, la, la, la
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:24.72,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,My voice out to forever
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:29.39,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already high, high, high
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:35.06,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Ride the dancing wind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:39.94,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,Sing, la, la, la
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:44.86,Ending Song,Ending Song,0000,0000,0000,,My voice springs up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.51,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,The typhoon left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.93,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:10.97,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-chan! Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:12.85,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun is here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:15.06,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,He's early again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.77,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:19.86,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.03,Main Dialog,Daikichi,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.48,0:22:23.03,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.82,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to open the storm windows...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:39.83,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Not a cloud in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:42.17,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.59,Main Dialog,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Kouki-kun, we're gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:46.92,Main Dialog,Kouki,0000,0000,0000,,See ya later!
